    </li>
    <li>Sistem komentar: <a href='https://waline.js.org' target='_blank'>Waline</a></li>
    <li>
      Kunjungan: <a href='https://supabase.com/' target='_blank'>Supabase</a> +
      <a href='https://waline.js.org/' target='_blank'>Waline</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      Statistik lainnya: <a href='https://github.com/spencerwooo/substats' target='_blank'
        >Substats</a
